<p class="has-foreground-color has-text-color" style="font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.455), 18px);">The Reserve Bank of India (RBI) has revised India&#8217;s GDP growth projection for FY2024, slightly lowering it due to global economic uncertainty, inflationary pressures, and domestic challenges. This revision has sparked discussions about the long-term sustainability of India&#8217;s growth trajectory.</p>
