<p class="has-foreground-color has-text-color" style="font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.455), 18px);">Delhi has been grappling with a severe spike in air pollution levels, with the Air Quality Index (AQI) reaching hazardous levels. Authorities have issued advisories to minimize outdoor activities and have increased efforts to control emissions from vehicles and construction sites.</p>
