<p class="has-foreground-color has-text-color" style="font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.455), 18px);">The Indian government has announced plans to roll out a national green hydrogen mission aimed at boosting the country’s renewable energy goals and reducing carbon emissions. This initiative aligns with India&#8217;s commitments to achieving net-zero emissions by 2070.</p>
