<p class="has-foreground-color has-text-color" style="font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.455), 18px);">India has played a significant role at the G20 summit, pushing for greater global cooperation on issues like climate change, economic recovery post-pandemic, and debt relief for developing countries. India&#8217;s leadership at the summit has highlighted its growing influence on the world stage.</p>
