<p class="has-foreground-color has-text-color" style="font-size:clamp(14px, 0.875rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.455), 18px);">A controversial statement by a senior leader of the Bharatiya Janata Party (BJP) has sparked widespread political debate. Opponents are criticizing the remarks, which they believe could inflame religious tensions, while BJP supporters are defending the leader&#8217;s freedom of speech.</p>
